					Full Description



		Computer Warehouse Group Plc is a Nigeria-based company, which offers Openmall platform. The Company's Openmall platform aggregates and displays the products and services of all the merchants and stores created on its e-commerce solution. The Openmall platform has various categories of products, and enables online shoppers to buy products from various store owners in a marketplace. The Company offers its Smart Utility Solution (SUS) to electricity companies in order to manage and monitor energy flow to end users. Its SUS provides theft prevention solution, energy audit, demand side management, real time billing efficiency and network asset management. The Company offers cloud services, software services, managed services and information technology (IT) infrastructure service. The Company serves a range of sectors, including financial services institutions, telecommunications, government and utility. Its SMERP is an Enterprise Resource Planning platform.
» Full Overview of CWG.LG







