Company Overview of CWG Plc



Snapshot People




Company Overview
CWG Plc engages in the supply, installation, integration, maintenance, and support of computer equipment, e-payment hardware, and ancillary equipment in Nigeria and internationally. It operates through IT Infrastructure, Software, Communication and Integrated Equipment, and Managed and Support Service segments. The IT Infrastructure segment supplies, installs, and supports computer hardware, operating and middle ware systems, automated teller machines, etc. The Software segment provides services in software deployment, implementation and support, systems analysis, design and implementation, and smartcard applications, as well as offers training on the systems offered and other off-the-shelf ...
CWG Plc engages in the supply, installation, integration, maintenance, and support of computer equipment, e-payment hardware, and ancillary equipment in Nigeria and internationally. It operates through IT Infrastructure, Software, Communication and Integrated Equipment, and Managed and Support Service segments. The IT Infrastructure segment supplies, installs, and supports computer hardware, operating and middle ware systems, automated teller machines, etc. The Software segment provides services in software deployment, implementation and support, systems analysis, design and implementation, and smartcard applications, as well as offers training on the systems offered and other off-the-shelf packages. The Communication and Integrated Equipment segment offers VSAT and fiber connectivity, metropolitan area networks, wide area networks, local area networks, and systems integration services, as well as network communications support. The Managed and Support service segment provides internal and external clients managed/outsourcing services; and offers related accessories for equipment and service maintenance. The company was formerly known as Computer Warehouse Group Plc. CWG Plc was founded in 1991 and is based in Lagos, Nigeria.
Detailed Description


