CWG Plc Key Developments

CWG Plc and Infosys Strengthen Partnership with New Business Opportunities
Dec 9 16
CWG Plc is shoring up plans to strengthen its partnership with Infosys, even as it seeks to identify more opportunities in Africa that will be jointly pursued with the Indian ICT solutions company. CWG its partnership with Infosys has brought opportunities around new products such as youth banking, commerce net, biometrics, Finacle Assure and Finacle Analytics.


